Dear Josh,

In the example, try:

dat$slab.ref <- mapply(function(x,y,z) as.expression(bquote(.(x)*","^.(y)~.(z))), dat$author, dat$trial, dat$year)

In general, read ?plothmath, ?bquote, and ?mapply to understand how all of this works.

Best,
Wolfgang

